{
  "stem": "11801.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I could not form a friendship or an attachment, since the attachment would, again, you know, be-- be, in the end, a negative experience for me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- yeah, they-- I was told not to use my name, you know, which didn't sound Jewish, but it sounded German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I used my middle name, Margaret.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody was told to call me Margaret, and somehow nobody really asked why.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't seem to be a problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not have the kind of problems that someone who passed as a Christian had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, the-- the-- who had to go to church, and know all the catechisms, and know all-- know all the prayers and the signs and the crossing yourself at appropriate times.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I never knew-- to this day, I don't know why we were kept in hiding, but yet, not literally hidden.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since these children had visitors from the outside, I can't believe that these outside visitors were not aware of my existence.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they weren't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
